<h2 style='font-size:14pt;color:#003366;margin:28px 0 12px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:2px solid #003366'>6. Détail OPEX récurrent (annuel, post M+24)</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Poste</th><th>Minimal</th><th>Cible</th><th>Accéléré</th></tr>
